https://github.com/jbrownlee/Datasets/releases/download/Flickr8k/Flickr8k_Dataset.zip
Link for the Flickr8k-Dataset
For the training model used is RNN with top of CNN.
Here the model is trained with 8k images and saved the model.For testing pretrained model is used for given test images.
You can use microsoft conceptual captioning dataset with 1 lakh images that will take aproximate 6 hr. in Normal CPU,
or you can use VGG pretrained model also.
Enjoy:)
